== Overview ==
The upgraded version of the [[EM Syphon]], the MKII model can literally immobilize a target by draining its energy reserves.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Syphon MKII can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
